1
00:01:48,846 --> 00:01:50,233
Is something wrong, K’Chat?

2
00:01:50,513 --> 00:01:52,510
Why aren't you wiping down K’Ran like you usually do?

3
00:01:54,850 --> 00:01:56,273
It’s better if you do it.

4
00:01:56,693 --> 00:01:58,690
I have to go prepare the medicine for Dad now.

5
00:02:00,010 --> 00:02:00,540
Yes

6
00:02:13,950 --> 00:02:16,940
Why are you calling me right now?!

7
00:02:17,110 --> 00:02:18,593
I already gave you the money.

8
00:02:18,613 --> 00:02:20,173
People are going to find out!

9
00:02:22,553 --> 00:02:24,550
What do you mean, "Off with the old, on with the new"?

10
00:02:24,706 --> 00:02:26,550
Didn’t we already discuss this?

11
00:02:27,290 --> 00:02:28,753
Don’t get all sensitive to me.

12
00:02:29,093 --> 00:02:32,700
No matter what, Ranya’s real father is you.

13
00:02:34,020 --> 00:02:36,020
Come on... once this whole mess is over,

14
00:02:36,053 --> 00:02:37,813
I’ll come back to you.

15
00:02:38,850 --> 00:02:39,960
I love you.

16
00:02:42,646 --> 00:02:43,786
I have to hang up now.

17
00:02:44,380 --> 00:02:45,126
Yes, yes...

18
00:02:49,373 --> 00:02:50,246
What is this?!

19
00:02:50,770 --> 00:02:52,440
Oh, it’s the medicine.

20
00:02:52,486 --> 00:02:53,893
K’Chat asked me to take it to K’Wichai.

21
00:02:53,920 --> 00:02:54,880
She already prepared it.

22
00:02:56,250 --> 00:02:57,533
Give it to me.

23
00:02:58,010 --> 00:02:59,120
I’ll take it to him myself.

24
00:02:59,610 --> 00:03:00,200
Yes, ma’am.

25
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:35,986
Oh my god!

26
00:03:36,013 --> 00:03:37,693
K’Wichai! K’Wichai,

27
00:03:37,713 --> 00:03:39,553
what’s wrong?

28
00:03:39,580 --> 00:03:40,793
Is anyone here?!

29
00:03:40,820 --> 00:03:41,546
What happened?

30
00:03:42,330 --> 00:03:43,226
K’Wichai

31
00:03:43,410 --> 00:03:44,220
Dad!

32
00:03:44,386 --> 00:03:45,046
K’Wichai

33
00:03:45,073 --> 00:03:45,606
Dad!

34
00:03:45,653 --> 00:03:47,073
Dad! Dad!

35
00:03:49,070 --> 00:03:52,553
He just took his medicine and suddenly collapsed!

36
00:03:52,930 --> 00:03:54,080
K’Wichai!

37
00:03:54,340 --> 00:03:55,173
Dad!

38
00:03:55,180 --> 00:03:57,186
Dad... Dad!/ Please, don't let anything happen to him.

39
00:03:59,690 --> 00:04:00,933
Dad!

40
00:04:02,330 --> 00:04:03,213
K’Wichai!

41
00:04:03,246 --> 00:04:04,060
K’Wichai!

42
00:04:04,290 --> 00:04:05,626
Dad... Dad!

43
00:04:07,390 --> 00:04:08,173
คุณวิชัยคะ

44
00:04:08,193 --> 00:04:09,026
พ่อ!

45
00:04:09,790 --> 00:04:10,533
K’Wichai!

46
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:11,460
Dad!

47
00:04:42,233 --> 00:04:44,166
If I actually get to be the President,

48
00:04:46,200 --> 00:04:47,920
I’ve prepared everything for you.

49
00:04:50,610 --> 00:04:52,213
You’ll be the Vice President;

50
00:04:55,420 --> 00:04:56,960
we’ll get to work together.

51
00:05:01,710 --> 00:05:03,460
But even if you don't want to work,

52
00:05:04,950 --> 00:05:06,560
I’ve already set aside shares for you.

53
00:05:14,170 --> 00:05:16,360
Just let me keep my promise first, Dad.

54
00:05:19,400 --> 00:05:21,760
I already failed to do it for Mom once...

55
00:05:25,306 --> 00:05:27,310
why are you doing this to me too?

56
00:05:35,070 --> 00:05:36,293
Why, Dad?

57
00:05:43,770 --> 00:05:45,473
Come back and scold me like you used to, okay?

58
00:05:50,590 --> 00:05:51,740
I give up, Dad.

59
00:05:51,773 --> 00:05:53,540
Just come back and yell at me again... right now,

60
00:05:58,870 --> 00:06:00,406
I have no one left.

61
00:06:30,233 --> 00:06:31,180
Ranya.

62
00:06:37,113 --> 00:06:38,253
It’s okay.

63
00:06:48,610 --> 00:06:51,913
I know this isn't exactly the best timing...

64
00:06:52,450 --> 00:06:54,666
but your dad left some documents for you.

65
00:06:55,080 --> 00:06:57,000
Take a look when you have a moment.

66
00:06:57,140 --> 00:06:58,693
They’re the company’s guidelines.

67
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:26,000
but your dad left some documents for you.

68
00:07:26,666 --> 00:07:28,670
Take a look when you have a moment.

69
00:07:28,706 --> 00:07:30,033
They’re the company’s guidelines.

70
00:07:47,946 --> 00:07:50,030
It was just a hug between sisters to give you strength.

71
00:07:53,290 --> 00:07:55,233
Truly. I don’t think of it as anything more than that anymore.

72
00:07:56,810 --> 00:07:58,166
I know it’s impossible.

73
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:11,806
It’s good that you know it's impossible.

74
00:08:13,030 --> 00:08:14,980
We can only ever be sisters, and that’s that.

75
00:08:18,713 --> 00:08:20,286
As for the matter of...

76
00:08:22,650 --> 00:08:24,913
Dad wanted to appoint me as another successor...

77
00:08:26,910 --> 00:08:28,460
I really didn't know anything about it

78
00:08:29,730 --> 00:08:31,460
How could you not know, Ranya?

79
00:08:31,493 --> 00:08:33,526
I never once thought about stealing your position.

80
00:08:34,270 --> 00:08:36,126
The evidence is right there in the documents.

81
00:08:39,486 --> 00:08:41,040
You’re conspiring with your mother, aren't you?

82
00:08:41,380 --> 00:08:42,953
I’m telling the truth, P'Chat.

83
00:08:44,400 --> 00:08:46,533
I’ll swear on my life if I have to.

84
00:08:48,153 --> 00:08:50,150
I would never dream of betraying you.

85
00:08:56,973 --> 00:08:58,970
Ranya! You can’t just go making oaths like that.

86
00:09:01,210 --> 00:09:02,746
If you actually died,

87
00:09:05,270 --> 00:09:07,040
I wouldn't have anyone left.

88
00:09:19,220 --> 00:09:23,440
I’ll stay by your side, just like I promised.

89
00:09:28,313 --> 00:09:29,800
But that’s your mother we're talking about.

90
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:31,793
And this is you, P'Chat.

91
00:09:35,300 --> 00:09:36,633
Don’t worry.

92
00:09:38,040 --> 00:09:39,546
I’ll make sure of it.
